Package: metrics
Title: Metrics for Classification Tasks
Version: 0.2.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Erard", email = "erard.thomas@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/thoera/metrics
BugReports: https://github.com/thoera/metrics/issues
Description: This package implements a consistent interface to compute metrics for classification models. It also offers an easy way to visualize those metrics.
